HEADWORD: knockdown-dragout
<hw>knockdown-dragout</hw></mhw>
<pos>adj.</pos> <def>marked by extreme violence; -- of fights; also used
metaphorically of fierce contests; <as>as, a
<ex>knock-down-and-drag-out</ex> fight; a <ex>knockdown-dragout</ex>
competition for the browser market</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ferocious, fierce, knockdown-dragout,
tearing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

